author: sussman
msg: Mention ra_svn on Subversion's web pages.  Our bulleted feature-list
on the front page is browsed mainly by newcomers who want a quick
overview; we don't want to mislead them into thinking Apache is the
only option.  (Especially considering how often we get ssh FAQs.)
* index.html:  mention svnserve option in network-server bullet point.
* project_faq.html:  mention svnserver option in two FAQs.
